      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in solid mechanical and aesthetic shape. The exterior shines beautifully in the sunlight, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats have been regularly conditioned and show no rips or significant wear, and all interior electronics\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a consistent maintenance history including a recent oil change and brake inspection. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. It is a smoke-free, pet-free car that offers a comfortable and dependable ride for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
